><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"αὐτῷ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\">[...]Ω</span><span data-text=\"ζωῂ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζωή\">ΖΩΗ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"αἰώνιος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"αἰώνιος\">[.....]ΟΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Παυλὲνος\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Παυλῖνος\">ΠΑΥΛΕΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"αὐτῷ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\">ΑΥΤΩ</span><span data-text=\"ζωῂ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζωή\">ΖΩΗ</span><span data-text=\"αἰώνιος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"αἰώνιος\">ΑΙΩΝΙΟΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003456_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003456_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003456.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003456-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Rizzone 2009</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3673-587X\">Maria Barbieri</a></p>  <p>Paulinos (?). A lui (sia) la vita eterna! </p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3673-587X\">Maria Barbieri</a></p>  <p>Paulinos (?). To him (be) eternal life!</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 2009.0441 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a>  </li><li> 59.1111 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Rizzone 2009 436-437 no.4 fig.6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-3  80  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
